title: 329 - I Dropped the Ball
description:
In this episode, the guys alongside Jemal “The 9 To 5 King Millionaire” discuss continuously working on yourself and your craft despite being great at it. The gentleman describe examples that exemplify growth in their personal lives. 

14:33 - “Just because you are great, that doesn’t guarantee anything. You still have to take advantage of the opportunities given.”

27:34 - “If God puts people around you, you should make it appoint to learn from them.”

41:43 - What are you learning about yourself as you grow? Are you implementing those changes?
